34
00:02:26,190 --> 00:02:28,810
code of Unix, they have to be public domain.

35
00:02:28,810 --> 00:02:35,420
There are some companies like IBM who designed
AIX from scratch to look like Unix, but include

36
00:02:35,420 --> 00:02:39,590
none of the source code of Unix so that they
